summary: Business consultant in the area of supply chain management software with the experience of working with logistics service providers across Europe. I have been involved in different agile implementation projects, actively taken part in planning, development, deployment and testing of Transportation Management System and connected tools, such as cross-dock applications and finance software. The key skill is in-depth knowledge of the software and its integration capabilities, which enables me to provide diverse solutions to business needs of logistics companies. Being an active member of cross-functional teams, I have been contributing to software development by creating effective use cases through gathering and analyzing customer requirements.
